111
0:04:40.26,000 --> 0:04:42,000
And this is a fundamental basic property

112
0:04:42.26,000 --> 0:04:44,000
that we exploit

113
0:04:44.26,000 --> 0:04:47,000
with our technology.

114
0:04:47.26,000 --> 0:04:49,000
So let's show how we do that.

