0:10:54.26,000 --> 0:10:56,000
In hospitals,

259
0:10:56.26,000 --> 0:10:59,000
for new medical instruments;

260
0:10:59.26,000 --> 0:11:02,000
in streets for traffic control.

261
0:11:02.26,000 --> 0:11:05,000
Cars have LED-based headlights, LED-based back lights,

262
0:11:05.26,000 --> 0:11:07,000
and cars can communicate with each other

263
0:11:07.26,000 --> 0:11:1,000
and prevent accidents

264
0:11:10.26,000 --> 0:11:13,000
in the way that they exchange information.

265
0:11:13.26,000 --> 0:11:16,000
Traffic lights can communicate to the car and so on.

266
0:11:16.26,000 --> 0:11:19,000
And then you have these millions of street lamps

267
0:11:19.26,000 --> 0:11:22,000
deployed around the world.

268
0:11:22.26,000 --> 0:11:24,000
And every street lamp could be a free access point.

269
0:11:24.26,000 --> 0:11:26,000
We call it, in fact, a Li-Fi,

270
0:11:26.26,000 --> 0:11:28,000
light-fidelity.

271
0:11:28.26,000 --> 0:11:32,000
And then we have these aircraft cabins.

272
0:11:32.26,000 --> 0:11:36,000
There are hundreds of lights in an aircraft cabin,

273
0:11:36.26,000 --> 0:11:38,000
and each of these lights

274
0:11:38.26,000 --> 0:11:41,000
could be a potential transmitter of wireless data.

275
0:11:41.26,000 --> 0:11:44,000
So you could enjoy your most favorite TED video

276
0:11:44.26,000 --> 0:11:46,000
on your long flight back home.

277
0:11:46.26,000 --> 0:11:49,000
Online life. So that is a vision, I think, that is possible.

278
0:11:55.26,000 --> 0:11:57,000
So, all we would need to do

279
0:11:57.26,000 --> 0:11:59,000
is to fit a small microchip

280
0:11:59.26,000 --> 0:12:02,000
to every potential illumination device.

281
0:12:02.26,000 --> 0:12:05,000
And this would then combine

282
0:12:05.26,000 --> 0:12:07,000
two basic functionalities:

283
0:12:07.26,000 --> 0:12:09,000
illumination and wireless data transmission.

284
0:12:09.26,000 --> 0:12:12,000
And it's this symbiosis that I personally believe

285
0:12:12.26,000 --> 0:12:14,000
could solve the four essential problems

286
0:12:14.26,000 --> 0:12:17,000
that face us in wireless communication these days.

287
0:12:17.26,000 --> 0:12:19,000
And in the future,

288
0:12:19.26,000 --> 0:12:22,000
you would not only have 14 billion light bulbs,

289
0:12:22.26,000 --> 0:12:25,000
you may have 14 billion Li-Fis

290
0:12:25.26,000 --> 0:12:27,000
deployed worldwide --

291
0:12:27.26,000 --> 0:12:29,000
for a cleaner, a greener,

292
0:12:29.26,000 --> 0:12:31,000
